Japan to Finance Geothermal Project in Indonesia, Sankei Says

-- B y   T a k e h i k o   K u m a k u r a
-- 
2011-07-18T22:49:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-18/japan-to-finance-geothermal-project-in-indonesia-sankei-says.html
The Japanese government will provide
55 billion yen in loans to  Indonesia  to finance a geothermal
power project in the country, the Sankei newspaper said.   Three Japanese companies, including  Mitsubishi Heavy
Industries Ltd. (7011) , control 70 percent of the global market for
geothermal plants, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Takehiko Kumakura at 
 tkumakura@bloomberg.net  